Enhanced functionality in `fast_inject_service` to handle and display multi-selected property values effectively.

task.summary: Default task
Add EventMixin and ImageMixin for enhanced event and image handling in controllers
Add TimelineMixin and TimelineTab for enhanced timeline functionality in controllers. This is the first try to implement a timeline tab. No real functionality for now.
Enhance timeline functionality with improved event handling and visualization in controllers. further debugging.
Enhance timeline functionality with improved event handling and visualization in controllers. further debugging.
Add calendar lookup functionality and improve event data handling in timeline tab
Enhance timeline tab setup and data loading with improved error handling and event processing
Enhance timeline tab setup and data loading with improved error handling and event processing
Fix mouse move event handling to ensure widget updates correctly
Refactor calendar data retrieval to use properties for improved data access, both for setup event calendar and timeline calendar. Works kind of.

Enhance calendar and timeline integration by loading detailed calendar data before timeline events, ensuring accurate event positioning. Update timeline tab to accept calendar data for improved event display.

Enhance timeline widget with detailed calendar data integration, improving event visualization and marker accuracy based on zoom level. Update calendar data handling for better month and day marker rendering.
Enhance timeline widget with improved event update handling and geometry adjustments for better rendering. Add periodic updates to ensure visual consistency.
Fix day marker drawing logic and increase maximum zoom level for improved timeline detail

Add LLM integration and enhance node description handling
Introduced `LLMService` for node description enhancement using an LLM via API calls, with optional contextual data from connected nodes. Updated UI and initialization logic to support the feature. Additionally, removed `requirements.txt` and adjusted project settings for improved modularity.

Add LLM integration and text enhancement UI feature
Introduced `LLMService` for text enhancement using AI via API calls, with support for context-based node descriptions. Updated the text editor UI to include an "Enhance with AI" button and implemented backend functionality for handling enhancement requests. Added configuration support for API key, URL, and model specifications, alongside improved error handling and logging.

Add LLMService for enhanced node description and UI integration
Introduced `LLMService` to enhance node descriptions using AI via API calls, with support for context-based information from connected nodes. Updated the text editor UI to include an "Enhance with AI" button and implemented backend functionality for handling enhancement requests. Added configuration support for API key, URL, and model specifications, alongside improved error handling and logging.
Fix LLM response handling to return empty string instead of None on errors

Add prompt template service and enhanced description feature
Introduced a new PromptTemplateService for managing LLM prompt templates, enabling enhanced node descriptions through template-based approaches. Updated the LLMService to utilize this service, allowing for context-aware enhancements. Added a new UI dialog for configuring enhancement options, including template selection and focus type. Improved error handling and user feedback for empty descriptions.

Add error handling and logging to AI enhancement request process
Enhanced the _request_enhanced_enhancement method to include error handling and logging. Improved user feedback for template service access issues and added logging for exceptions during the enhancement request process. Updated the UI dialog to ensure a smoother user experience when configuring AI enhancement options.

Enhance LLM description handling and improve prompt template service
- Updated LLMService to require valid HTML responses with paragraph tags for enhanced descriptions. - Improved error handling and logging in the AI enhancement request process. - Refactored prompt template service to clarify instructions for generating engaging descriptions. - Adjusted UI to display both current and enhanced descriptions for better user feedback.

Enhance LLM description handling and improve prompt template service
- Refactored enhance_node_description to utilize a default template for enhancements. - Added error handling for missing templates in the prompt template service. - Updated LLMService to support template-based enhancements with improved parameter handling. - Introduced YAML-based template loading for better flexibility and maintainability.

Enhance LLM description handling and improve prompt template service
- Refactored enhance_node_description to utilize a default template for enhancements. - Added error handling for missing templates in the prompt template service. - Updated LLMService to support template-based enhancements with improved parameter handling. - Introduced YAML-based template loading for better flexibility and maintainability.
Refactor logging statement for improved readability in node operation service
Refactor LLMService and prompt template service for improved context handling and error management
Refactor enhancement process by removing focus type parameter and improving template preview functionality
Refactor prompt templates by removing focus type parameters and adding a new physical description template
Refactor project configuration files to update documentation format and enhance workspace settings
Implement line feature properties dialog and enhance map tab functionality with line drawing support
Implement line feature properties dialog and enhance map tab functionality with line drawing support

Enhance line feature with labels and interaction handling
Added hoverable labels to lines, styled similarly to pin labels, and enabled their visibility on hover. Refined event handling for line clicks and improved label positioning and scaling based on zoom level.

Add line editing functionality with interactive controls
Implemented edit mode for lines, allowing users to modify existing lines directly on the map. Added control points for precise line vertex manipulation and options to insert or edit points via context menus. Updated geometry handling and UI components to support smooth integration of editing features.

Add line editing functionality with interactive controls
Implemented an edit mode for map lines, enabling users to modify lines directly with control points for vertex manipulation. Added new constants to streamline visual styles, hit detection, and geometry handling. Updated the map widget for better scaling, customization, and integration of editing features.

Refactor line handling into modular components.
Extracted line rendering and persistence logic into separate modules for improved modularity and maintainability. Enhanced line editing functionality with control point interactions, better rendering, and streamlined geometry updates. Updated related constants and UI components for consistency and scalability.

Refactor map component for modularity and simplification
Reorganized map-related classes into separate modules to improve code modularity and maintainability. Simplified `map_tab.py` by extracting line rendering, image loading, and drawing logic into dedicated components. This enhances readability, scalability, and future development efficiency.

Modularize dialogs for map components
Extracted `PinPlacementDialog` and `LineFeatureDialog` into standalone modules for improved structure and reusability. Refactored `map_tab.py` to reflect these changes, enhancing maintainability and code organization.

Add branching line drawing functionality to map feature
Introduced branching line drawing mode with UI toggle support in `map_tab.py`. Added necessary handling for branching lines, including toggle status, point addition, and rendering preparation. Enhanced `line_container.py` to support modular line features required by the new functionality while improving code readability and error handling.

Refactor prompt templates and enhance line management logic
Updated `prompt_templates.yaml` to include a new "Create Plant Description" template with detailed formatting and processing instructions. Refactored line scaling and geometry management in `line_geometry.py` and related components to improve modularity, ensure accurate scaling with dynamic image dimensions, and enhance debugging capabilities. Added comprehensive logging to aid in debugging and maintaining feature consistency throughout the map component hierarchy.

Add functionality to branch lines from nearest points
Introduced a feature to start new branches from the nearest existing points in branching line drawing mode. Enhanced `DrawingManager` and `MapTab` to calculate the closest points based on user interactions and seamlessly create new branches. Improved visual debugging with updated drawing styles, point markers, and feedback for branch creation.

Add branching line configuration dialog for map component
Introduced a dialog to configure branching line features, including target node selection, line style customization, and WKT geometry preview. Integrated the dialog into the map component to enhance branching line creation workflow and improve user interaction.

Enhance map component with improved edit mode integration
Added initialization for an enhanced edit mode in the map component, improving user interaction workflows. Updated XML and log entries to reflect new configurations, ensuring better tracking of recent activities and changes.

Add enhanced edit mode integration for map component
Integrated an improved edit mode for the map component, enhancing edit workflows and adding better diagnostic tools. Refactored branching line handling to use the enhanced feature manager when available, improving feature flexibility and logging for better debugging. Updated workspace configuration to reflect these changes.

Enhance map component edit mode and update workspace config
Connected enhanced features to controller's pin click handler and improved feature click event handling for branches. Updated workspace and coverage configurations to reflect changes in the enhanced edit mode and related tests.

Refactor to rename and streamline feature management components
Renamed `unified_feature_manager.py` to `feature_manager.py` for clarity and updated references accordingly. Improved code formatting and organization, including refactoring multiline statements for readability. Cleaned up unnecessary whitespace and redundant code, ensuring consistency across map component handling.

Refactor and enhance fast inject functionality
Renamed and streamlined feature management components for clarity and consistency. Updated fast inject service to support JSON templates and added a new herb template with comprehensive properties. Improved UI file selection to support multiple file types and enhanced code structure for readability.

Refactor property search and improve query handling.
Introduced support for handling array properties in Neo4j queries, ensuring consistent behavior across all property types. Enhanced code readability by adding safe fallbacks, clarifying parameter usage, and improving clause construction. Simplified project filtering logic with a default literal value. This is a static search on a property list.

Refactor property search and enhance property type handling.
Added dynamic property discovery to differentiate between array and scalar types, enabling improved query construction in Neo4j. Enhanced query builders to handle diverse property types with better error handling and code clarity. Updated methods to refresh property types and ensure consistent search functionality.

Switch property inputs from radio buttons to checkboxes
Replaced radio buttons with checkboxes to support multi-selection in property value input. Updated related UI methods for handling checkbox inputs, preserving selections, and editing property values. Enhanced functionality in `fast_inject_service` to handle and display multi-selected property values effectively.
